Author: linkercoin
Title: âš¡ðŸš€ðŸ”¥[ANN][LNC] Sign up for BITNARU and get LNC airdropped! ðŸ”¥ðŸš€âš¡
Body: Linker Coin(LNC) is planning on a bounty program before it burns Foundationâ€™s 20 Million LNC  - Burn Foundationâ€™s 20 Million LNC every month - total of 200 Million will be burned, 40% of total LNC issued  -Purchase 10 Million LNC in Exchange until 1st quarter of next year, 2019    What is Linker Coin, the 'Network of Networks?'  Linker Coin is a platform where it connects between fiat currencies and cryptocurrencies.   It successfully ended its ICO at the end of last year and was recently listed in its own exchange, BITNARU.    For the detailed description on Linker Coin(LNC) please refer to our Homepage and white paper. Links below.    Homepage: https://www.linkercoin.com/      White Paper: https://docs.wixstatic.com/ugd/4e7588_b2bbea7c99e54b37a4c51b7b823971a5.pdf      Linker Coin Official Telegram:  https://t.me/linkercoineng      What is 'BITNARU,' global exchange to link digital assets?   - LinkerCoin foundation's own Exchange  - Exchange with TUSD as a key currency  - Able to trade in Korean Won (KRW) Market  - 1 Million order per second possible and Maker commission: -0.01%  - Financial technology company, Alpha Point, participated in developing BITNARU  (Alpha Point is a company which developed core engine for well-known exchange Bitfinex and is responsible for supporting liquidity  in BITNARU from Kraken, and Bitfinex)  BITNARU exchange homepage: https://www.bitnaru.com/  -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------    <Bounty Program Introduction>  Bounty Program Dates: until 13th of August, 2018  Distribution Date: On the next LNC burning date next month  Distributed To: Participants in Bounty Program until the official LNC burning date in August 2018  Distribution Method: Distributed directly to your BITNAUR LNC wallet      <<<<<<<<<<How to Participate>>>>>>>>>>   New members:  1) Sign up for an account at BITNARU : https://bitnaru.com  2) Join Linker Coin official Telegram : https://t.me/linkercoineng (Must introduce yourself upon joining)  3) Follow official Linker Coin Twitter + BITNARU Twitter  >Linker Coin Twitter: https://twitter.com/Linkercoin  >BitNaru Twitter: https://twitter.com/bitnaru  4) Post comments about your participation on this post down below  5) Finally, submit Google Form for participating in this bounty program  * Above 5 steps MUST  all be executed in order to receive 150 LNC, no distribution of LNC until all 5 steps are done.     Existing Members:  1) Follow Linkercoin Twitter + BITNARU Twitter & Like and Retweet more than 1 post  >LinkerCoin Twitter: https://twitter.com/Linkercoin  >BitNaru Twitter: https://twitter.com/bitnaru  2) Follow Linker Coin Official Medium page & like more than 5 posts  >LinkerCoin Medium: https://medium.com/linkercoin  3) Post comments about your participation on this post down below  4) Finally, submit Google Form for participating in this bounty program  *All 4 steps MUST be done before you can receive 150 LNC, no distribution of LNC until all 5 steps are done.   <<â€»LNC Bounty Program Participation Formâ€»>>  https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd2BI1j6OuFwj-111FFhpKXKxbjVWapt1Im3VIvbbBiIu6vcA/viewform   <<â˜žFor any inquiriesâ˜œ>>  Please leave a comment down below, or visit our official Telegram.    https://t.me/linkercoineng  -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------  <<<<<<<<<<â€»LNC Bounty Program Extentionâ€»>>>>>>>>>>  LinkerCoin is going to burn 20 Million LNC on August 30th.  Thanks to the enthusiastic support and attention from participants,  We decided to extend this bounty event,  which was scheduled until August, to August 30th in line with the LNC  burning on August.  After the bounty program is finished, the distribution will be done during the first week of September.  Please participate in our bounty event and keep supporting us.  Thank you. [/size]  -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------  <<<<<<<<<<<<<LINKERCOIN Announcement>>>>>>>>>>>>>[/b]  Regarding the LinkerCoin burning schedule, it is changed to that about 40% of the total volume will be burned in the first quarter of next year.  Detailed information on the LinkerCoin burning schedule: â†“â†“â†“â†“â†“ https://medium.com/linkercoin/ann-information-on-linkercoin-burning-schedule-voting-result-679924704afd  The first Bounty program is ended and the payment will be made in order by 20th September. Bounty payment schedules will be paid sequentially by September 20.  Thank you for your interests and participation. We are planning to have the 2nd Bounty Promotion at the end of September for Bitnaru renewal. Please look forward to the 2nd Bounty Promotion.
